want to use BuddyPress for your community.</p>\n<p></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Director / DP / Editor &#8211; <a href="http://vimeo.com/gilbertomartinez">Gilberto Martinez</a></li>\n<li>Composer &#8211; Ivan Barbou</li>\n<li>eMarketing strategy/campaign developed and conducted by Stephen Byrne, Marina Dias de Castro, Gilberto Martinez, Everett Parkins, and Jayme White, at Capilano University School of Business.</li>\n<li>Thanks to Teresita Barbou, Enrique Jahn, and Cyri Jones.</li>\n</ul>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 25 Oct 2012 00:51:42 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"John James Jacoby";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:48;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:13:"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:37:"Alex King: WordPress Community Summit";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:28:"http://alexking.org/?p=14881";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"http://alexking.org/blog/2012/10/24/wordpress-community-summit";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:876:"<p>I&#8217;m quite looking forward to the <a href="http://make.wordpress.org/summit/">WordPress Community Summit</a> next week. I&#8217;m hoping to lobby for a few of <a href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=%21closed&reporter=alexkingorg">my pet core tickets</a> while I&#8217;m there, but I&#8217;m particularly looking forward to some of the discussion topics and the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unconference">unconference</a> format. An unconference works great when you have the right people, and this should be exactly the right situation for it.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;m heading out for the weekend too and will be playing a few rounds of golf. Looks like the timing is excellent.</p>\n<p><img src="http://alexking.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/weather.png" alt="" title="weather" width="480" height="286" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14882" /></p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 24 Oct 2012 21:41:32 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Alex";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:49;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:13:"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"Weblog Tools Collection: WordPress Theme Releases for 10/24";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/?p=12139";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~3/M-5uLssoaSs/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1484:"<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-12142" title="harmoni" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/harmoni.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://arifqodari.co.de/features/"><strong>Harmoni</strong></a> is a simple and clean theme with a responsive layout.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-12140" title="neutral" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/neutral.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://emptynestthemes.com/2012/10/23/neutral-wordpress-blog-theme/"><strong>Neutral</strong></a> is a professional looking and attractive theme that lives up to its name, with a neutral color scheme that includes taupe or beige, white and gray with a very readable and clean sans serif font for the main body text, and an attractive script for the headings to add just a touch of personality.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-12141" title="stripefolio" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/stripefolio.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/stripefolio"><strong>Stripefolio</strong></a> is a free clean theme designed to function both as a readable blog and website as well as a fullscreen portfolio showcase for designers, painters, artists, photographers, etc.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/M-5uLssoaSs" height="1" width="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 24 Oct 2012 14:45:10 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"James";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:"type";i:128;s:7:"headers";a:9:{s:6:"server";s:5:"nginx";s:4:"date";s:29:"Mon, 05 Nov 2012 07:27:03 GMT";s:12:"content-type";s:8:"text/xml";s:14:"co